<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <%- include('../Global/google.ejs'); %>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex,nofollow">
    <title>Download <%= episode.drama_name %> Episode <%= episode.epno %>
    </title>

    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
        integrity="sha384-1BmE4kWBq78iYhFldvKuhfTAU6auU8tT94WrHftjDbrCEXSU1oBoqyl2QvZ6jIW3" crossorigin="anonymous">

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.1.0/css/all.min.css"
        integrity="sha512-10/jx2EXwxxWqCLX/hHth/vu2KY3jCF70dCQB8TSgNjbCVAC/8vai53GfMDrO2Emgwccf2pJqxct9ehpzG+MTw=="
        crossorigin="anonymous" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" />

    <%- include('./partials/style.ejs'); %>
    <%- include('../Global/nav-style.ejs'); %>
    <%- include('../Global/ads/style.ejs'); %>
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('../Global/navhtml.ejs'); %>
    <h1 style="width: 98%; margin: 12px auto; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold;">
        Download <%= episode.drama_name.split('(20')[0] %> - Episode <%= episode.epno %>
    </h1>

    <div class="ad">
        <%- include('../Global/ads/300x250.ejs'); %>
    </div>

    <div class="ep-us">
        <div class="heading">
            <i class="fa-brands fa-telegram"></i>
            DOWNLOAD SECTION
        </div>
        <div class="epinfo">
            <% if (user.userId == '1006615854') { %>
            <%- include('./partials/bestie.ejs'); %>
            <% } else { %>
            <h4>Dear
                <b>
                    <%= user.fname.substring(0,22) %>
                </b>,
            </h4>
            <% } %>
            <h5>You're about to download
                <b>
                    <%= episode.drama_name.split('(20')[0] %> <br>
                    Episode <%= episode.epno %>
                </b>
            </h5>
        </div>
        <br>
        <div class="progCont" id="progCont">
            <div class="progress" role="progressbar" aria-label="Animated striped example" aria-valuenow="100"
                aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100" style="height: 32px;">
                <div class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped progress-bar-animated" id="prog" style="width: 100%">
                    0%
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="divButton" id="divButton" style="display: none;">
            <button onclick="sendEpis()" id="btnEp">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-download"></i>
                GET YOUR EPISODE (<%= episode.size %>)
                <i class="fa-brands fa-telegram"></i>
            </button>
        </div>
        <div class="preparing"><span id="counting">00%</span></div>
    </div>

    <br>
    <div class="ad">
        <!-- ad here -->
    </div>
    <br>


    <div class="userinfo">
        <h6><u>About You</u></h6>
        <ul>
            <li>Telegram Username: <%= user.fname.substring(0,22) %>
            </li>
            <li>Total Episode downloads: <%= user.downloaded %>
            </li>
            <li>Total Points: <%= user.points %> pts.</li>
            <li>Last activity: <%= user.last %>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="usersWetu">
        <%- include('./partials/table.ejs'); %>
    </div>

    <hr class="style-eight">
    <div class="article">
        <h5><u>7 Possible Ways of Making Money Online</u></h5>
        <p>
            <b>1. Freelancing:</b> Freelancing allows you to offer your skills and services to clients online.
            Whether you're a writer, graphic designer, programmer, or marketer, there are numerous freelancing
            platforms where you can find gigs and earn money.
        </p>
        <p>
            <b>2. E-commerce:</b> Setting up an online store and selling products or services is another popular way
            to make money online. Platforms like Shopify or WooCommerce make it easy to create and manage your
            online business.
        </p>
        <p>
            <b>3. Affiliate Marketing:</b> Affiliate marketing involves promoting other people's products and
            earning a commission for every sale or lead generated through your referral. You can join affiliate
            programs of various companies and promote their products through your website or social media.
        </p>
        <p>
            <b>4. Online Surveys:</b> Many companies pay individuals for participating in online surveys and
            providing feedback. While the earnings may not be substantial, it can be an easy way to make some extra
            money in your spare time.
        </p>
        <p>
            <b>5. Content Creation:</b> If you have a passion for creating content, you can monetize it through
            platforms like YouTube, podcasts, or blogging. With a dedicated audience, you can earn money through
            ads, sponsorships, or by selling your own products.
        </p>
        <p>
            <b>6. Online Tutoring:</b> If you have expertise in a particular subject, you can offer online tutoring
            services. Platforms like Tutor.com or VIPKid connect tutors with students, allowing you to teach and
            earn money from the comfort of your home.
        </p>
        <p>
            <b>7. Online Investments:</b> Investing in stocks, cryptocurrencies, or other online investment
            opportunities can potentially generate passive income. However, it's important to do thorough research
            and understand the risks associated with online investments.
        </p>
        <p>
            Remember, success in making money online often requires time, effort, and dedication. It's essential to
            choose a method that aligns with your skills and interests, and be prepared to adapt and learn as you go
            along.
        </p>
    </div>
    <footer>
        <span>
            Korean Drama Store
        </span>
        <span class="a" onclick="window.open('tg://join?invite=mTx_t-6TBx9hNTc8', '_self')">
            <i class="fa-brands fa-telegram"></i> Join Us Telegram
        </span>
        <span id="dated">
        </span>
    </footer>

    <%- include('./partials/script.ejs'); %>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
        integrity="sha384-ka7Sk0Gln4gmtz2MlQnikT1wXgYsOg+OMhuP+IlRH9sENBO0LRn5q+8nbTov4+1p"
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

    <%- include('../Global/ads/vignette.ejs'); %>
</body>

</html>